---
name: agentkaggle-opt-sol
version: 1
schema: omhflow/v1
models:
  roles:
    coordinator: rustcat/gpt-5.6-sol:xhigh
    implementer: rustcat/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    repair: rustcat/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    architect: infini/claude-opus-4-8:xhigh
    planner: rustcat/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    functionalReviewer: infini/claude-opus-4-8:xhigh
    reviewer: infini/claude-opus-4-8:xhigh
    searchA: rustcat/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    searchB: infini/claude-opus-4-8:xhigh
  defaults:
    agent: coordinator
    review: reviewer
  unavailable: fail
checkpoint:
  stopDeadlineMs: 300000
changePolicy:
  agentsCanPropose: true
  humansCanApprove: true
---
# AgentKaggle Campaign Optimization

```yaml workflow
